Package cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.algorithm

Package contains basic classes and interfaces required to define new algorithms.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Algorithm Common interface for all algorithms.
ChainAlgorithm Chain algorithms can continue work of other algorithm by giving them a configuration to work on.
 

Class Summary
BaseAlgorithm Implements some methods of Algorithm identical for most algorithms.
 

Exception Summary
CannotContinueException This exception is raised whenever algorithm is unable to continue.
InvalidProblemException This exception is raised when algorithm is run on problem it cannot solve.
 

Package cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.algorithm Description

Package contains basic classes and interfaces required to define new algorithms. Subpackages contains implementations of some basic algorithms, such as graph search (DFS, BFS), SA, GA.
